{"tid":917154,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[再開post][陳詠謙]如流行歌曲加上李力持 如蓮蓉屎沾污了靚泳池 (原曲︰周國腎 - 理智與感情)","createTime":"2018-11-26T08:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T13:25:30.000Z","uid":68884,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2e641958e4fa1364f3710f1b39790e74e1d3b952","tid":917154,"uid":68884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T08:08:13.000Z","msg":"之前開過post但打錯歌名，而家再開，希望有巴打肯唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n詠謙 詠謙佢一朝得志<br />\n詠謙 詠謙佢不懂寫作 亂試<br />\n每首歌堆砌字句全沒意義<br />\n詠謙 詠謙放開手一試<br />\n詠謙 詠謙佢癡Q咗線<br />\n歌詞 騎呢修辭 <br />\n令偉文亦覺得羞恥<br />\n<br />\n一首歌曲 寫得再美好<br />\n歌手的音準感情再好<br />\n要是涉及你 都很糟糕<br />\n<br />\n如流行歌曲加上李力持<br />\n如蓮蓉屎沾污了靚泳池<br />\n無能何必假裝高深故意<br />\n還越來越見自負做幕前<br />\n首首歌有你份詞<br />\n還維護廣東歌 哪個願意<br />\n陳姓詠謙這個毒瘤確實唔掂<br />\n你填詞不過二線"},{"pid":"13dc829400516f45f7a7a0131df7a5e961bba908","tid":917154,"uid":104658,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T08:09:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我現時自己肯做飯</span>"},{"pid":"61ba1f4a9c742512585bf2fd9514d5c0f3c2245f","tid":917154,"uid":68884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T12:18:18.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e07283022a341809b9934a820f4aa65986278c","tid":917154,"uid":105343,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:22:12.000Z","msg":"巴打邊間教會"},{"pid":"3fc9eb287c00f6e61cb0b3994fef1749b5008179","tid":917154,"uid":25435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:25:30.000Z","msg":"我們身邊太多<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">假人</span>"}]}